<h2>Showing a Node</h2>
<p>By default, Node instances are hidden using the CSS <code>display</code> property.  Calling the <code>show</code> method displays the node.</p>
```
    Y.one('#demo').show();
```

<h2>Hiding a Node</h2>
<p>The opposite of <code>show</code>, the <code>hide</code> method sets the node's CSS <code>display</code> property to <code>none</code>.</p>
```
    Y.one('#demo').hide();
```
